dia/jersey-media-json-jackson/2.35/execution-metrics.json` reports 13 iterations and dynamic-access coverage `1/1` (100.00%).\n\nRecommended manual follow-up:\n- Review the preserved branch and confirm the generated tests plus the new metadata entries for `RuntimeDelegateImpl` and `JaxbAnnotationIntrospector` are acceptable.\n- Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.glassfish.jersey.media:jersey-media-json-jackson:2.35` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.glassfish.jersey.media:jersey-media-json-jackson:2.35` in an environment with sufficient free `/tmp` space.\n- If those checks stay green, continue from the preserved branch instead of regenerating from scratch."}}
